Considerations and analysis of the implementation of oncogeriatrics in Chile and 
its importance: Review of current literature.

Honorato M(1), Calderón O(1)(2), Rojas V(1), Fasce G(3)(4), Bartolotti C(5)(6), 
Caglevic C(7).

Author information:
(1)Geriatrics Department, Clínica Alemana de Santiago, Santiago, Chile.
(2)Geriatrics, Complejo Asistencial Dr Sótero del Río, Santiago, Chile.
(3)Geriatrics Service, Department of Medicine, Hospital Clínico Universidad de 
