Response inhibition and error-monitoring in cystinosis (CTNS gene mutations): 
Behavioral and electrophysiological evidence of a diverse set of difficulties.

Francisco AA(1), Foxe JJ(1)(2)(3), Berruti A(1), Horsthuis DJ(1), Molholm 
S(1)(2)(3).

Author information:
(1)The Cognitive Neurophysiology Laboratory, Department of Pediatrics, Albert 
