Funding Life-Extension Research.

Khan M(1).

Author information:
(1)Hevolution Foundation, KAFD, Riyadh 13519, Saudi Arabia 
m.khan@hevolution.com.

While the worldwide trend in life expectancy continues to increase slightly 
overall, the trend for the last few decades in developed countries is that more 
people are spending more years in poor health with multiple chronic 
comorbidities. These chronic conditions in aging populations consume high 
